@page "/"

<PageTitle>FreiService - Holy Days Calculator</PageTitle>

<h1>FreiService - Holy Days Manager</h1>

<div class="row mt-4">
    <div class="col-md-8">
        <p class="lead">
            Welcome to the FreiService Holy Days Manager - a comprehensive tool for calculating and managing 
            Christian liturgical calendar dates.
        </p>

        <h2 class="mt-4">Features</h2>
        <ul class="list-group mb-4">
            <li class="list-group-item">
                <strong>🗓️ Calculate Holy Days</strong> - Compute Easter and related movable feasts using the 
                Meeus/Jones/Butcher algorithm
            </li>
            <li class="list-group-item">
                <strong>👁️ Dry Run</strong> - Preview holy days for any year before committing to the database
            </li>
            <li class="list-group-item">
                <strong>💾 Save to Database</strong> - Store calculated holy days in SQLite for future reference
            </li>
            <li class="list-group-item">
                <strong>📋 Manage Data</strong> - View, update, or delete saved holy days by year
            </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="mt-4">Supported Holy Days</h2>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Easter Sunday</strong> - The principal feast of the Christian calendar</li>
                    <li><strong>Ash Wednesday</strong> - First day of Lent (46 days before Easter)</li>
                    <li><strong>Pentecost</strong> - 50 days after Easter</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Trinity Sunday</strong> - First Sunday after Pentecost</li>
                    <li><strong>Annunciation of Mary</strong> - March 25 (fixed date)</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="alert alert-info mt-4" role="alert">
            <strong>💡 Getting Started:</strong> Navigate to the <a href="/holydays" class="alert-link">Holy Days Manager</a> 
            to begin calculating and managing holy days for any year from 1583 onwards.
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="card bg-light">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Quick Facts</h5>
                <dl>
                    <dt>Algorithm</dt>
                    <dd>Meeus/Jones/Butcher</dd>
                    
                    <dt>Valid Range</dt>
                    <dd>1583 - 9999</dd>
                    
                    <dt>Database</dt>
                    <dd>SQLite</dd>
                    
                    <dt>Precision</dt>
                    <dd>100% accurate for Gregorian calendar</dd>
                </dl>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
